{
  "stem": "25639.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And immediately, she ran for the pile of books and she-- she hid it under her garter belt, under her skirt.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when the Gestapo looked everywhere, they couldn't find a trace of the book.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's what-- the books, and that's what they were looking for.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everything else was very well hidden at all times, covered up in a way that it was not possible for them to see it easily.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- but her father was, nevertheless, sent to a concentration camp for two years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when he came out, he had to go to the Gestapo every week to report.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "47 Years before that, we would go into our barracks, and-- hoping to get a good night's sleep and get away from the monsters that we dreamt about.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And instead, we had to meet the punishment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we never knew who was going to be punished.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, of course, as it worked out, we just cried for the other person, because this was-- [CRYING] it was very difficult to see.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't talk about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were all subjected to some of this periodically.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'd like to move on, however, from Hannover, where I was taken to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Hamburg, I did, again, street work, helped keep the-- clear the rubble from the major streets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember we were right by the harbor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, there was-- the alarm could be heard very often throughout the day and night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The-- this meant that the Allies were bombing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, of course, wherever we looked, we could see Hamburg destroyed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once in a while, people would pop up from basements and suddenly they were there.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
